ley 0-1.\n| goals2     = M Daly 0-5, G Keane 0-4, F Lohan 0-1, J Enright 0-1.\n| stadium    = [[Gaelic Grounds]], [[Limerick]]\n| referee    = N Barrett ([[County Cork|Cork]])\n| attendance = \n| stack      = yes\n}}\n\n{{16TeamBracket-Compact-NoSeeds-Byes\n| RD1=Preliminary Round\n| RD2=Quarter-final\n| RD3=Semi-finals\n| RD4=Final\n| score-width= 45\n| group1=\n| group2=\n| RD1-seed01=\n| RD1-team01=[[Limerick GAA|Limerick]]\n| RD1-score01=1-13<br>2-08\n| RD1-seed02= \n| RD1-team02='''[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]'''\n| RD1-score02=0-16<br>'''1-17'''\n| RD2-seed01=<!--Replay-->\n| RD2-team01='''[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]'''\n| RD2-score01='''2-7'''\n| RD2-seed02=\n| RD2-team02=[[Waterford GAA|Waterford]]\n| RD2-score02=1-5 \n| RD3-seed01=\n| RD3-team01='''[[Kerry GAA|Kerry]]'''\n| RD3-score01='''2-12'''\n| RD3-seed02=\n| RD3-team02=[[Tipperary GAA|Tipperary]]\n| RD3-score02=1-10\n| RD3-seed03=\n| RD3-team03='''[[Clare GAA|Clare]]'''\n| RD3-score03='''2-13'''\n| RD3-seed04=\n| RD3-team04=[[Cork GAA|Cork]]\n| RD3-score04=1-14\n| RD4-seed01=\n| RD4-team01='''[[Kerry GAA|Kerry]]'''\n| RD4-score01='''1-13'''\n| RD4-seed02=\n| RD4-team02=[[Clare GAA|Clare]]\n| RD4-score02=0-11\n}}\n\n===[[Leinster Senior Football Championship]]=== \n\n'''First round'''\n\n{{footballbox collapsible \n| date       = 11 May 1997\n| round      = First round\n| team1      = [[Wexford GAA|Wexford]]\n| score      = 2-5 - 0-11\n| team2      = [[Westmeath GAA|Westmeath]]\n| goals1     = J Lawlor 1-1, M Mahon 1-0, L O'Brien 0-3, B Kirwan 0-1.\n| goals2     = K Lyons 0-3, M Flanagan 0-3, T Cleary 0-3, O Keating 0-1, G Heavin 0-1.\n| stadium    = [[O'Kennedy Park]], [[New Ross]]\n| referee    = S McCormack ([[County Meath|Meath]])\n| attendance = 2,000\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible \n| date       = 11 May 1997\n| round      = First round\n| team1      = [[Offaly GAA|Offaly]]\n| score      = 5-17 - 0-13\n| team2      = [[Longford GAA|Longford]] \n| goals1     = A Kelly 1-3, R Malone 1-2, C McManus 1-2, V Claffey 1-1, C Quinn 1-0, P Brady 0-3, F Cullen 0-2, S Grennan 0-1, R Mooney 0-1, J Grennan 0-1, V Mooney 0-1.\n| goals2     = D Barr 0-6, E Barden 0-3, E McCormack 0-3, T Smullen 0-1.\n| stadium    = [[O'Connor Park]], [[Tullamore]]\n| referee    = A Walsh ([[Dublin]])\n| attendance = 18,000\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible \n| date       = 17 May 1997\n| round      = First round replay\n| team1      = [[Westmeath GAA|Westmeath]]\n| score      = 2-17 - 1-15\n| team2      = [[Wexford GAA|Wexford]]\n| goals1     = M Staunton 1-2, T Cleary 0-4, P Conway 1-0, G Heavin 0-3, S Colleary 0-2, M Treanor 0-2, J Murray 0-2, M Flanagan 0-1, J Cooney 0-1.\n| goals2     = J Byrne 0-8, S Dolan 1-1, Lawlor 0-4, Doran 0-1, Guinan 0-1.\n| stadium    = [[Cusack Park (Mullingar)|Cusack Park]], [[Mullingar]]\n| referee    = \n| attendance = \n| stack      = yes\n}}\n\n'''Second round'''\n\n{{footballbox collapsible \n| date       = 25 May 1997\n| round      = Second round\n| team1      = [[Offaly GAA|Offaly]]\n| score      = 0-8 - 0-8\n| team2      = [[Westmeath GAA|Westmeath]]\n| goals1     = V Claffey 0-4, P Brady 0-2, R Mooney 0-1, C McManus 0-1.\n| goals2     = T Cleary 0-7, J Cooney 0-1.\n| stadium    = [[O'Connor Park]], [[Tullamore]]\n| referee    = P O'Toole ([[Longford]])\n| attendance = 11,000\n| stack      = yes\n}} \n{{footballbox collapsible \n| date       = 7 June 1997\n| round      = Second round replay\n| team1      = [[Westmeath GAA|Westmeath]]\n| score      = 0-7 - 1-14\n| team2      = [[Offaly GAA|Offaly]]\n| goals1     = T Cleary 0-5, P Conway 0-1, G Heavin 0-1.\n| goals2     = D Reynolds 0-6, P Brady 1-2, V Claffey 0-2, C McManus 0-1, J Kenny 0-1, R Mooney 0-1, M Daly 0-1.\n| stadium    = [[Cusack Park (Mullingar)|Cusack Park]], [[Mullingar]]\n| referee    = P O'Toole ([[Longford]])\n| attendance = 11,000\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n\n'''Quarter-finals'''\n\n{{footballbox collapsible \n| date       = 1 June 1997\n| round    